1) Book Selection -- Power System Quality Assessment
Author: Arrillaga
Power supply quality and its delivery has become especially important in light
of current deregulations taking place throughout the world. The increased use
of power semiconductor devices in industrial, commercial, and domestic
electronic equipment has led to forms of harmonic pollution, all of which are
dealt with in this important reference.
